Package management

Interface DataManager<T1,T2>

Type Parameters:
T1 - the type of the Object associated to the data manager
T2 - String associated to the data manager
All Known Implementing Classes:
AppointmentDataManager, InventoryDataManager, MedicalBillDataManager, MedicationRequestDataManager, PatientDataManager, ReplenishmentDataManager, StaffDataManager
public interface DataManager<T1,T2>
A generic interface that accepts two types: T1 for Object and T2 for String.
